: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\">CHAT ONLINE NGAY</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n', '2018-01-10 04:28:24');

